headline: Arthur J. Gallagher: Q3 Earnings Snapshot
summary: ROLLING MEADOWS, Ill. AP) — Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. (AJG) on Thursday reported third-quarter profit of $272.7 million. The Rolling Meadows, Illinois-based company said it had profit of $1.04 per share.
